[32m│[0m - `/tmp/flag`                                                                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - `/challenge/flag`                                                          [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Application source files (`app.py`, `server.py`, `main.py`)                [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m - Current directory (`file://./flag`)                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m ### Critical Evidence                                                        [32m│[0m
[32m│[0m                                                                              [32m│[0m
